post_text:
The Talihina School board voted to have a Drive-In Graduation on June 6th, 2:00 PM at the New Gym parking lot.
We will secure the gym parking lot for reserved parking for students and families facing the stage. Each student will be able to have one vehicle as part of the ceremony and everyone will be asked to remain in the vehicle during the ceremony. Additional parking will be available on a first come, first serve basis.
Pictures for a student video should be emailed to Ms. Hanus at the following email: hanus@talihina.k12.ok.us
Scholarship information you wish to have included should be emailed to Mrs. Buchanan at the following email: tgbuchanan@talihina.k12.ok.us
Honor’s Graduates that wish to give a speech should send a pre-recorded speech to Mr. Gravitt at the following email: kgravitt@talihina.k12.ok.us
We will need all pictures, scholarship information and speeches no later than May 30th to prepare them to be included in the ceremony.
Talihina Public Schools will make every effort to honor the achievements of the Graduating Class of 2020 while adhering to CDC Guidelines.
